      "content": "hey so i was cutting up some veggies and the knife slipped really bad on my forearm. its a pretty deep cut and it’s kind of oozing blood and clear fluid like it won't stop. do u think i can just clean it out and put some honey on it and bandage it up? i really dont want to go to the clinic if i dont have to",
