      "content": "i know but the clinic here is so far and the wait is always like 4 hours :( i've heard so much about medicinal grade honey being amazing for healing wounds and preventing infection naturally. if the bleeding slows down a bit, can't i just use that to keep it clean instead of waiting all day at the doctor?",
